normal warder clearing takes ~30 mins for 1-2 SoDs, 3-4 1h primals (and 2hers, other trinkets like gnome mask)<br>
<br>
post-awakening sleeper takes about 45 mins - 1 hour for prog and MotG, about 50% chance overall for ONE 1h primal...maybe 25% for 1hp, and even lower for 1hb...shrouds, SoDs gone permanently, replaced by gimp prismatic scales quests ... oh and if you're desperate for primal, as most guilds are in ST after awakening, you can take an hour and a half or two hours to clear down to FA for a small chance at another primal<br>
